name: Rome is not a town (se)
description:
Rome Is Not A Town from Gothenburg (Sweden) debuted in 2015 with the single Stupid and has since released several EPs and the debut album Itâ€™ s a Dare (2017) which established them as one of the most distinctive voices in Swedish indie rock.

Live, their music explodes and pulls the audience in from the very first note. With a powerful, magnetic energy, the band takes over the room and refuses to let go. The new album Echoes of Love (2026) marks a clear and confident step forward. Still familiarly intense and uncompromising, but with a new sharpness and greater seriousness.
